generator = EmpiricalBayesThompsonSampler(min_weight=0.0)
generator.fit(Xs=self.Xs, Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.Yvars, parameter_values=
    self.parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
f, cov = generator.predict([[1, 1], [3, 3]])
self.assertTrue(np.allclose(f, np.array([[1.3, 0.25], [2.9, 0.25]])))
self.assertTrue(np.allclose(cov, np.array([[[1.03, 0.0], [0.0, 0.375]], [[
    0.87, 0.0], [0.0, 0.375]]])))
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    generator.predict([[1, 2]])
